      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project or parts donor. The engine currently has significant trouble starting and runs very roughly, while the exterior shows heavy wear, including several dents and faded paint. The interior also requires a deep clean and repair of torn upholstery. It is being sold strictly as-is with no guarantees on its roadworthiness.",
