      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a valuable source of parts? This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision to take the reins! While it currently requires extensive mechanical and cosmetic restoration to return to its former glory, it serves as a great foundation for a dedicated builder or DIY expert. Grab this opportunity to breathe new life into a classic silhouette!",
